Write a program to print all even numbers between 1 and N (inclusive).

Input Format

A single integer N

Constraints

1 ≤ N ≤ 1000

Output Format

Print all even numbers separated by space.

Sample Input 0

10
Sample Output 0

2 4 6 8 10
Sample Input 1

7
Sample Output 1

2 4 6 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
#include <math.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main() {
    
    int n;
    scanf("%d",&n);
    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++){
        if (i%2==0)
            printf("%d ",i);
    }
    return 0;
}


